short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Stash, Retrieve & Organize links in collections called Projinks.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Projinks is a Google chrome extension that allows you to stash your browser links in collections called "Projinks". Useful for research, team projects, personal link library, and keeping order of places and things of interest on the web you come across. Projinks is the best alternative to bookmarking. Projinks offers you more control for the right online experience.
